{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1721503, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 338539, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不要着急，先慢慢考虑清楚\n家里需要你寄生活费回家吗，不需要的话没关系，工科直博可以不从家里要生活费养活自己", "timestamp": 1621916727, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1721507, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 338539, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "直博不是还有点补贴呢么，顺便兼个职", "timestamp": 1621916747, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1721515, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 338539, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不要，勇往直前。两年后，如果不妙，再转硕走人。", "timestamp": 1621916795, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1721517, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 338539, "reply_to": 1721503, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 家里还有房贷，父亲告诉我他去开滴滴赚钱应该基本能收支相抵。但目前如果遇上急需用钱的情况家里肯定就撑不住了", "timestamp": 1621916817, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1721522, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 338539, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "记住现在不要对外说自己在读博，而是要读硕。", "timestamp": 1621916838, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1721523, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 338539, "reply_to": 1721515, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 理科院系，不好转硕", "timestamp": 1621916839, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1721548, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 338539, "reply_to": 1721523, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 好转的，这个放心。要真不能转，读个博士，不亏的。任何人家都没有那么脆弱的，关键你要尽量不浪费时间，找好导师，平安度过博士生涯", "timestamp": 1621917089, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1721549, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 338539, "reply_to": 1721548, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 谢谢C君鼓励，我再考虑一下", "timestamp": 1621917134, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1721565, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 338539, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "如果负债累累，三思。想清楚为什么读博，拿什么支撑读博，生活和科研压力两头压下来。", "timestamp": 1621917346, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1721566, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 338539, "reply_to": 1721549, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 理科院系可以当助教？助教2600+学校固定2810+导师发的，一个月六七千，一个月应该可以存上四千？一年也有几万，不遇到突发大事应该够了\n一些文素课也会面向全校招助教，我工科师兄就去了\n突发急需用钱的情况只能说概率应该不高，真遇到了工作一两年的积蓄也未必顶用", "timestamp": 1621917371, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1721618, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 338539, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不至于，哪怕想办法恰点儿烂钱，生活还不至于艰难", "timestamp": 1621917949, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1721634, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 338539, "reply_to": 1721566, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 精准解释了", "timestamp": 1621918159, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1721647, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 338539, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "F君是得知父亲生病了提前一年毕业工作 理解dz", "timestamp": 1621918396, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1721744, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 338539, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "楼里都是很孝顺很有责任心的人，可以！好样的！", "timestamp": 1621919632, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1721888, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 338539, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "谢谢诸位回复", "timestamp": 1621921106, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1722152, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 338539, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "读博同时带家教，一月赚个3w不难，也超过你清本科生就业的平均工资了。把最难的一段时间熬过来就好，dz加油！", "timestamp": 1621925664, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1791542, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 338539, "reply_to": 1722152, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 同觉得可以去当家教", "timestamp": 1622868939, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 4, "pid": 338539, "reply": 17, "tag": null, "text": "今天得知父亲也下岗失业了，考虑要不要退掉直博名额赶紧准备工作", "timestamp": 1621916604, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1622868936, "url": "", "vote": {}}}